739
00:39:29,663 --> 00:39:31,665
Hindi ba dapat ikaw
nag-aaral para sa iyong pagsusulit?

740
00:39:32,327 --> 00:39:33,995
Napakabagal mo, Cuz!

741
00:39:34,365 --> 00:39:35,365
Hindi ba ito gumagana?

742
00:39:35,390 --> 00:39:39,436
Kailangan mong patuloy na manood ng marami
mga pelikula upang patalasin ang iyong kakayahan sa pag-arte.

743
00:39:39,982 --> 00:39:41,483
Isa akong acting CEO, kung tutuusin.

744
00:39:41,538 --> 00:39:42,537
ha?

745
00:39:42,562 --> 00:39:43,335
ano?

746
00:39:43,361 --> 00:39:44,561
Grabe, tignan mo yung pinsan natin.

747
00:39:45,241 --> 00:39:46,409
Hindi mo ito nakuha.

748
00:39:46,657 --> 00:39:48,450
Kahit ano, Cuz.

749
00:39:49,283 --> 00:39:50,409
Anong mga pelikula ang dapat kong panoorin?

750
00:39:51,156 --> 00:39:52,282
Ughh.

751
00:39:53,591 --> 00:39:55,426
Hoy, irekomenda mo ako
ilang pelikula, okay?

752
00:39:56,072 --> 00:39:57,237
Oo, sigurado, sigurado.
Iisipin ko ang ilan.

753
00:39:57,262 --> 00:39:58,514
I-update kita kaagad.

754
00:40:00,196 --> 00:40:02,740
<i>Ohayo gozaimasu!</i>
Goodmorning!

755
00:40:03,380 --> 00:40:05,549
<i>Sugoi desu neee!!!</i>
Wow, ito ay mahusay!

756
00:40:05,663 --> 00:40:07,164
<i>Anata washi!</i> Ikaw at Ako!

757
00:40:08,690 --> 00:40:10,400
<i>Anata wa kudasai?</i>
PARA SAYO... PLEASE.

758
00:40:12,166 --> 00:40:14,085
Wow, sarap talaga
parang nasa Japan ako.

759
00:40:14,331 --> 00:40:15,475
Siyempre,

760
00:40:15,500 --> 00:40:16,834
