Nanalo ba ako sa lotto
nang hindi nalalaman?

789
00:41:40,018 --> 00:41:43,564
At itong restaurant
ay itinayo nang napakabilis.

790
00:41:44,231 --> 00:41:45,232
Masyado kang nagsasalita.

791
00:41:45,482 --> 00:41:47,151
Kung gayon paano ito naging akin?

792
00:41:47,234 --> 00:41:50,070
Hindi mo ba nabasa ang
kasaysayan ng korporasyon?

793
00:41:57,327 --> 00:41:58,537
Templo ng Umami.

794
00:42:00,122 --> 00:42:00,831
Tama!

795
00:42:00,832 --> 00:42:03,625
Nabasa ko ang tungkol diyan
restaurant sa dossier!

796
00:42:03,987 --> 00:42:07,031
Ito ay binibigkas
“doh-see-yay,” hindi “dosee-yer.”

797
00:42:08,547 --> 00:42:09,547
“Doh-see-yay?”

798
00:42:09,965 --> 00:42:10,965
Oh, ganyan?

799
00:42:10,990 --> 00:42:11,990
Ang cute niyan.

800
00:42:12,251 --> 00:42:13,669
Parang masaya.

801
00:42:14,185 --> 00:42:16,041
Doh-see-yay!

802
00:42:16,066 --> 00:42:17,865
Doh-see-yay!

803
00:42:17,890 --> 00:42:18,890
Doh-see-yay.

804
00:42:18,915 --> 00:42:20,876
Doh-see-yay!

805
00:42:22,674 --> 00:42:23,674
Dossier.

806
00:42:27,331 --> 00:42:28,873
<i>Konnichiwa!</i>
Hello!

807
00:42:28,898 --> 00:42:32,652
<i>Kuchira magamoto salmon sashimi,</i>
Narito ang iyong tuna at salmon sashimi,

808
00:42:32,901 --> 00:42:37,781
<i>Yumunikotoroniko No Teriyaki Seto,</i>
Ang mga set ng beef at chicken teriyaki,

809
00:42:38,229 --> 00:42:41,357
<i>Yoshoto Yo Karifornia Maki.</i>
At ang aming bahay espesyal na California maki roll.

810
00:42:42,426 --> 00:42:44,971
<i>Gozaimasu!</i>
Masiyahan sa iyong pagkain.

811
00:42:46,710 --> 00:42:49,338
<i>Katoke Nihonjarake?</i>
Akala ko ba Japanese restaurant ito?

812
00:42:50,005 --> 00:42:52,925
Nande Karifornia ga aru no?
Bakit mayroon kang California?

813
00:42:53,763 --> 00:42:54,763
Jaram!

814
00:42:55,348 --> 00:42:56,348
Jaram!

815
00:42:56,373 --> 00:42:57,373
Jaram!

816
00:42:59,787 --> 00:43:00,680
Hai!

817
00:43:00,705 --> 00:43:01,705
Hai!

818
00:43:13,237 --> 00:43:14,357
Anong kalokohan ang ginagawa mo?

819
00:43:16,165 --> 00:43:18,209
Pinaghihiwalay ko ang
galing sa bigas.

820
00:43:24,127 --> 00:43:25,127
Naku, Zeke!

821
00:43:25,722 --> 00:43:26,807
Ito ay hilaw!

822
00:43:26,990 --> 00:43:27,990
Hindi ito luto.

823
00:43:28,015 --> 00:43:29,391
Oo, salmon sashimi iyon.

824
00:43:30,404 --> 00:43:31,447
Hindi ka pa nagkaroon niyan?

825
00:43:31,956 --> 00:43:35,609
I’m more of a grilled-food-girly
Wala kaming masyadong alam tungkol dito

826
00:43:35,634 --> 00:43:36,634
hilaw na pagkain.

827
00:43:43,172 --> 00:43:43,692
Hoy!

828
00:43:43,774 --> 00:43:44,774
Hoy, huwag!

829
00:43:44,926 --> 00:43:45,926
Wag mong kainin yan!

830
00:43:46,799 --> 00:43:47,799
anong ginagawa mo

831
00:43:48,060 --> 00:43:49,644
Nakita mo na ito ay hilaw.

832
00:43:49,669 --> 00:43:50,789
Bakit kinakain mo pa?

833
00:43:51,430 --> 00:43:52,722
Baka sumakit tiyan mo mamaya.

834
00:43:52,747 --> 00:43:53,414
Baka magkasakit ka.

835
00:43:53,439 --> 00:43:54,439
Fine, suit yourself.

836
00:43:54,642 --> 00:43:55,642
Itigil mo na.

837
00:43:55,890 --> 00:43:56,890
Ito ay ligtas.

838
00:44:25,316 --> 00:44:27,276
meron ako
importanteng itanong sayo.

839
00:44:30,230 --> 00:44:31,356
Oh, ano ito?

840
00:44:33,115 --> 00:44:35,951
Alam mo ba kung ano
ibig sabihin ng salitang "Mafia"?

841
00:44:38,047 --> 00:44:39,047
Mafia?

842
00:44:40,782 --> 00:44:42,284
Hindi. Ano ito, tinapay?

843
00:44:43,587 --> 00:44:44,921
Ang tanging alam ko lang ay,

844
00:44:46,011 --> 00:44:48,639
Pork <i>Hopia</i>, Mung Bean <i>Hopia</i>,

845
00:44:49,207 --> 00:44:50,709
Gourd <i>Hopia</i>.

846
00:44:51,460 --> 00:44:52,586
O isda?

847
00:44:55,047 --> 00:44:56,047
Tilapia ba?

848
00:44:56,089 --> 00:44:57,089
Idiot!

849
00:44:58,216 --> 00:44:59,216
Seryoso ako.

850
00:45:01,553 --> 00:45:03,805
Naranasan mo na ba
narinig ang salitang iyon?

851
00:45:05,535 --> 00:45:06,099
Hindi.

852
00:45:06,100 --> 00:45:07,100
Ano ang mafia?

853
00:45:11,396 --> 00:45:13,315
Ito ay isang organisadong grupo ng mga tao

854
00:45:13,674 --> 00:45:15,551
na nagpapatakbo ng mga kumplikadong operasyon

855
00:45:15,738 --> 00:45:18,241
na karamihan sa mga tao ay hindi
makita o alam man lang.

856
00:45:19,446 --> 00:45:23,825
Lahat ng kasali sa mafia
ay inaasahang sumunod sa isang panuntunan:

857
00:45:24,826 --> 00:45:25,826
para mabuhay.

858
00:45:26,828 --> 00:45:30,832
Kaya naman lagi nilang kailangan
upang maging tuso at walang awa.

859
00:45:36,046 --> 00:45:39,007
So ibig sabihin mafia
ang mga tao ay mga kriminal?

860
00:45:43,303 --> 00:45:45,179
Oo, kung gusto mo
upang ilagay ito sa paraan.

861
00:45:45,180 --> 00:45:46,180
Oo naman.

862
00:45:46,305 --> 00:45:50,935
Pero parang pamilya na sila
na nabubuhay sa pamamagitan ng isang code.

863
00:45:53,039 --> 00:45:54,873
Pumapatay ba sila ng tao?

864
00:45:54,898 --> 00:45:58,068
Oo, kung mayroon sila
upang ipagtanggol ang kanilang sarili.

865
00:45:59,567 --> 00:46:00,735
Pagkatapos ay iyon mismo.

866
00:46:00,791 --> 00:46:02,127
Mga kriminal sila.

867
00:46:03,468 --> 00:46:07,889
Ngunit ginagawa nila ang kanilang ginagawa
kailangang gawin para mabuhay.

868
00:46:09,453 --> 00:46:10,453
Kahit na ano!

869
00:46:11,248 --> 00:46:12,957
Pumapatay pa rin sila ng tao,

870
00:46:12,958 --> 00:46:15,252
ibig sabihin sila
walang puso.

871
00:46:16,044 --> 00:46:19,256
Hindi nila gagawin ang mga iyon
bagay kung sila ay mabuting tao.

872
00:46:27,514 --> 00:46:28,514
Bakit, Zeke?

873
00:46:30,392 --> 00:46:31,432
Parte ka ba ng mafia?

874
00:46:41,194 --> 00:46:42,946
Aalis ka na sa kumpanya
kay Aemie diba?

875
00:46:43,113 --> 00:46:44,113
Oo.

876
00:46:44,197 --> 00:46:45,824
Huwag mong maliitin ang asawa ko.

877
00:46:45,991 --> 00:46:48,659
Tungkol saan ang itinext mo sa akin

878
00:46:48,660 --> 00:46:50,245
kumikilos bilang isang CEO?

879
00:46:50,579 --> 00:46:51,579
Oh!

880
00:46:51,997 --> 00:46:54,624
Magsisimula yan pagkatapos ni Zeke
alis bukas.

881
00:46:55,333 --> 00:46:57,053
- Gusto mo bang tulungan kita?
- Maaari mo ba akong tulungan?

882
00:46:57,669 --> 00:46:59,337
talaga? Tutulungan mo ako?!

883
00:46:59,588 --> 00:47:01,274
- Oo naman.
- Huwag mong nakawin ang spotlight ko, okay?

884
00:47:01,298 --> 00:47:02,174
Pero binabalaan kita.

885
00:47:02,257 --> 00:47:04,468
Wala akong pasensya pagdating sa...

886
00:47:04,718 --> 00:47:05,760
kakulangan.

887
00:47:07,262 --> 00:47:09,598
Kakulangan?!

888
00:47:10,807 --> 00:47:11,807
Hoy!

889
00:47:13,810 --> 00:47:15,395
Dapat ko bang tawagan ang doktor?

890
00:47:15,479 --> 00:47:16,455
Fiona.

891
00:47:16,480 --> 00:47:17,480
kamusta ka na?

892
00:47:17,505 --> 00:47:20,842
At ang pinaka masayang honeymoon
sa buong kasaysayan!

